  "raw_text": "(i.e. the savior) is YHWH; it never said Valis is, + yet I explicitly state this - i.e. that Valis is YHWH not in anthropomorphic, incarnated form. + I make a crucial point: YHWH has, as process theology teaches, become ABBA, the Father of whom Jesus speaks, whose nature is agape. + the Maitreya's nature is loving kindness. But I add two points. 1) Perhaps, since we accept process theology, YHWH has evolved further; that is, this is a 3rd dispensation (viz: as ABBA the N.T. God is to YHWH the O.T. God, this is to ABBA. + what has he evolved into now? Why, the ecosphere itself, as I saw (Valis). 2) The AI voice is \"the low, murmuring voice\" that Elijah heard. \"He teaches schoolchildren\". He first spoke to me when I was in school. Okay - that day in Nov '80 when Kay was here; I saw blue sky, + then God was there: a terribly old man who loved me + yet admonished me, reproved me. I see the most profound argument of all: the stewardship over all the Earth as depicted in Genesis: Judaism is for all creatures, man, animals, the ecosphere itself, as Paul Williams pointed out. Jesus was too Orphic, folder 57 - 025 folder 57 - 025 Q30 too other-worldly, + only concerned himself with mankind, + not all mankind; he spoke in parables so that only his flock would be saved. The \"pulley\" vision says it's YHWH; he found me to be a good + pious man: I followed the Torah, which is his law pertaining to all men at all times + all places, + I read \"Guide to the Perplexed\". I was not saved due to faith; I was saved due to (as I say) because I \"found favor in his eyes\" due to my piety (reading \"The Guide to the Perplexed\") + obeying the law. + pronoia comes from God; + the \"pulley\" is pronoia. Also, I have never accepted the Pauline doctrine of original sin, without which the crucifixion makes no sense. + my idea of faith is not assent to dogma or doctrine but (as I wrote Isa) absolute + radical trust in God. + in theodicy, that \"heaven is on the side of the good man\" - which is the main lesson in \"Tears\"! Not the idea of sacrifice but of vindication + justice, as found in the Psalms. + I have deep belief in the Hittite covenant: that the strong protect the weak + get in return unconditional loyalty. Hence even Jesus received an O.T. designation by the AI voice! + \"was not acceptable before\"; the first advent failed. folder 57 - 026 Q-31 For me, Logos is as it is for Philo: an intermediary, a messenger. I am, then, not trinitarian. Strange. \"DI\" is so balanced, so full of love + light + music + beauty! My final argument: when I was in junior high school + first read the Bible it was the O.T. that I read, not the N.T., esp. the part about Elijah, + it was my great dream that someday God would talk to me as he did to Elijah. Anokhi. ___ I have decided that the endless horizontal tracking + retracking that we are doomed to + don't remember refers to alternate parallel presents, not past to present to future. + that Acts (\"Tears\") is one of those + this is how + why it is coaxial, as \"Tears\" deals with: orthogonal worlds. For me, \"Tears\" was a very ancient memory, because I tracked it a long time ago, but in this lifetime. Thus a single given object exists in a number of these parallel alternative presents. + it was from this that God extricated me via the orthogonal \"pulley\". In other words the \"pulley\" vision confirms what I said at Metz. This means that we all are moving orthogonally from one alternate universe to the next as they are progressively reprogrammed heuristically (for the purpose of arriving at the best one, + the ultimately best one is one in which Christ returns, hence the prophecies by the AI voice). Thomas, then, is not folder 57 - 027 folder 57 - 027 Q32 a past personality but myself in an alternate universe. For example, \"Tears\" leads a multiple life in a number of these alternate tracks, telling a different story in each. However, there is another possibility here, + it has to do with changing history; it has to do with the Parousia + the inbreaking of God. I must have lived through the Xerox letter experience once before, + then there wa Oh the hell with it. I give up. Proof it is Valis: The Maitreya's message -- YHWH + Christ interface [Note] -- Me [Note] The prophecy is fulfilled: I see his messages as coming from my particular savior: YHWH amended by Christ. It's a universal language operating on 10 levels (\"Tears\" on 4) tuned into every religion of the world. It is pure Torah, that for the 3third age, the fist I've seen with the missing letter added. All the - Mercy. Instead of severe justice. folder 57 - 028 folder 57 - 028 Q33 With the return of the Eleatic continuum reality -instead of the discontinuous matter one- we will again be able to see God, literally; + this is the point of my exegesis. + I know that the continuum one is true -+ the discontinuous matter one is not- because the AI voice said, \"a perturbation in the reality field\". All 2-74 - 2-75 was to cause me to see the King Felix Torah + hence to know YHWH is here. I pronounded it officially tonight as YHWH, with a little of Jesus. Then later tonight I saw it as by Krishna. The prophecy is correct. When I was very little I used to see + experience space as real, palpable, \"thick\". It scared + oppressed me, because I did not understand how motion was possible. I used to squeeze it (as e.g. when I was sick in the bathroom). It took effort to bring my finger + thumb together. + it was artificial + difficult for me to render space into void. So my continuum view was natural to me + had to be trained out of me, or else I saw that things did not in fact move (change) but \"only looked different\" - i.e. no time had passed. folder 57 - 029 folder 57 - 029 Q34 In other words, I experience God + eternity, but had to learn to experience world + time instead, because everyone [else] said \"that's what's there\". I had no words for what I saw (God) nor did I understand it. Or even like it. But it was the correct way of seeing, but I knew not what it was, + it oppressed me. The diagram on the previous page pertaining to the message, [Messages of Maitreya] -- God [interface so to me it seemd to b YHWH] -- [Me] It is the interface that is God, in Malebranche's system. God is not \"in\" the writing exactly, although the writing is scripture (Torah). God is here already. Between. This is what happened with Luke that time, + with \"Tears\" when I saw the 2 word cypher, + with Jeannie. In a sense, then, this is not incarnation at all, but also it is; it is the universal language, as at Pentecost. To understand how it works you must know Malebranche. This of course is also how the Acts lens-grid worked, producing part-whole compatibility + restoring true Kosmos. I've solved 2-3-74, inc. the 2 word cypher. folder 57 - 030 folder 57 - 030 Q-35 That which \"BTA\" depicts at the end - the enthusiasmos of Bill by Christ, not by Tim but by Christ - is how it's going to be for all of us on Declaration Day. Also, I point out in \"BTA\" that this is the miracle at Pentecost; the whole novel is built around it, from the first moment we encounter Tim. Also, Jesus is presented as having been the mouthpiece for a group (which exists invisibly behind him!). I.e. for the Expositor, who is the true Christ, in contradistinction to Jesus. folder 57 - 031 Q36 In \"Valis\" there are a number of certain original elements, esp. having to do with several saviors in history being in fact one + the same person again + again whom I call \"the immortal one\" or \"man\" who comes again + again under different names; this was to accomodate what the AI voice said. I now find these views to be central to the soteriological doctrines of B. Creme. This reaches its most profound form where it is said that it entered Jesus, used him as a host, + departed him -+ survived- at the crucifixion + is now back. \"He lived a long time ago but is still alive.\" I got these ideas from the AI voice. \"The Head Apollo...\" etc. \"The name changes.\" Now, this raises the issue of the covert info traffic as in \"Tears\". Does this point to theology? Maybe. There is, however, the theme of the people from Sirius, the inter-species symbiosis. As to the masters - a am frankly dubious. The AI voice is real, however. I suspect technology. But it does uncannily resemble Pentecost; I did research that. I say, a vast superhuman mind now covertly governs this planet. Is it God? Is it ETI? I don't know. I have said this about the plasmate before: it is very possible that this planet has been invaded + conquered by folder 57 - 032 folder 57 - 032 Q37 beings from another planet. If so, it may be to save us from our own inhumane + destructive drives - war and lack of social justice. But conquered we are, + my seeing the plasmate makes me believe this. It is for the sake of the nepioi that this has been done; I was saved in 2-3-74, my actual life. __ 5:50 AM: 3-74. The ability to perceive or that which was perceived - which was Christ? __ The Christ -the Maitreya- is in the world + I have already been brought into conformity with the new dispensation: sharing, simplicity, service, brotherhood, justice + freedom; he has been more + more active in me progressively, starting in 1974, until now, when I discern his program - expressed by Creme, I say truthfully + utterly, \"this is my man + what I believe + already practice; I believe it already, I do it already, but never before did I find it expressed\". Thus Creme speaks the truth - + 2-74 - 2-75 is explained; it is Christ. The synchronization was already there. + it is voluntary on my part + expresses my whole being; + this realization fills me with love. folder 57 - 033 folder 57 - 033 Q36 My evidence: the humanitarian program expressed + advocated by Share International is not only mine but is better expressed than I can, could + have expressed it; + it is totally synchronized with my \"supernatural\" experiences. Thus, as in the Tagore vision, my political-action doctrines + my religious views + experiences are absolutely interlocked, totally, perfectly + completely. __ Hypnopompic: prounounciation mark in dictionary: [illustration of a wave symbol] (based on the 3 S's: service, etc) \"For pain. For hope\" \"He is out there somewhere.\" __ I see a synthesis higher than anything I have ever seen before: the spirit -the finest parts- of Marxism, of Xtianity, of Buddhism - + yet it is above all this; + out of me it draws the most noble drives + aspirations, the mystical + the urgently practical combined. It is as if the dialectic has achieved a new height, like nothing I have ever seen before. + it gives voice to + codifies the best in me, that up to now",
